name: BABY ANGEL GHOST
description:
story: war has started, and he died in peace, he is a hero with great strength, but half of his strength is stored in his bones so he can rise again but when his soul is looking for his body he is trapped in the multiverse of darkness, making evil forces attack him, darkness wants immortality, and now he's back but possessed by a dark creature, look at him so scary. And do you know whose skull he's holding? it's his mother!
but why is he holding his mother's skull? only time can answer

greetings from me: so guys, I want to let you know that this is my last series from "baby angel verse" where in this series there are Easter eggs from the previous series,thank you if you already have the series before, and please also remember, all these baby angel are interconnected, so I hope you also have other series so that it becomes your complete collection where the series consists of:

BABY ANGEL WITH FLAMINGO WINGS

BABY ANGEL VILLAIN

BABY ANGEL ASTRONAUT

and closed with
BABY ANGEL GHOST

collect everything, take care of him to be a big angel.
